perl-PPI (perl module for PPI)

Parse, Analyze and Manipulate Perl (without perl)  

required perl: Params::Util, Clone, Task::Weaken, List::MoreUtils, IO::String
required SBo: perl-Params-Util, perl-Clone, perl-Task-Weaken, perl-List-MoreUtils, perl-IO-String

More possible libraries:
  http://search.cpan.org/~chorny/Hook-LexWrap-0.24/
  http://search.cpan.org/~adamk/Test-SubCalls-1.09/
  http://search.cpan.org/~adamk/Class-Inspector-1.24/
